  "title": "Lifetime income and old age mortality risk in Italy over two decades",
  "abstract": "The evidence on the shape and trend of the relationship between (lifetime) income and old age mortality is scarce and mixed both for North American and European countries. Nationwide evidence for Italy does not exist yet.",
